docs.abstract: With performances on pause, many dancers are rethinking their relationship to weight.
docs.snippet: With performances on pause, many dancers are rethinking their relationship to weight.
docs.lead_paragraph: Like many ballet dancers, Lauren Lovette has had some questions during the pandemic. One keeps rising to the top of her list. What is a ballet body? And a corollary: What does healthy look like? “Am I really working on being a better dancer?” Lovette said. “Or am I just trying to starve and get skinnier, so now I have the line?”

headline.print_headline: Second Thoughts on the Ballet Body

docs.abstract: The museum’s first triennial, imperfect but stimulating, has successfully landed.
docs.snippet: The museum’s first triennial, imperfect but stimulating, has successfully landed.
docs.lead_paragraph: For much of the past year, New York City’s museum clock has been running on Covid time. When lockdown hit last March, exhibitions in progress went dark. Some later reopened for a last-gasp run. Others never saw the light again. Still others, originally scheduled to debut during the past several months, have had to carve out new slots. “Estamos Bien — La Trienal 20/21” at El Museo del Barrio, is one of the late-landing arrivals.

headline.main: El Museo Looks to Define ‘Latinx Art’ With a Major Survey

headline.main: Menthol Cigarettes Kill Many Black People. A Ban May Finally Be Near.

docs.abstract: Nearly all of the big winners from the evening are available to stream. Here’s a look at where to find them and what The Times first had to say about them.
docs.snippet: Nearly all of the big winners from the evening are available to stream. Here’s a look at where to find them and what The Times first had to say about them.
docs.lead_paragraph: During a normal year, when many of the awards-contending movies are released late in the season, home viewers often have to wait for a month or two to catch the winners on various streaming services. But the one benefit to an awards show during a pandemic year is that all the winners are immediately available — or so we might have assumed.

headline.main: Golden Globes 2021: Where to Stream the Winners
